abstract: Jelena Jankovic wins Guangzhou International title, beating Denisa Allertova in final round; Belinda Bencic beats top-seeded Caroline Wozniacki in Toray Pan-Pacific Open semifinals; other tennis news noted.
lead_paragraph: The former No. 1 Jelena Jankovic continued her strong form in China, beating Denisa Allertova, 6-2, 6-0, on Saturday to win the Guangzhou International title.

headline.print_headline: Sports Briefing | Tennis; Jankovic Wins Again in China
